{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/250909-playwright/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Lenny.dev"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a5338c39-bdb0-5989-9737-114cc839567c","excerpt":"안녕하세요. 프론트엔드하면서 부끄럽게도 테스트코드 작성이라는걸 말만 들어봤지 해본적이 없네요. 부끄럽네요 ㅋ 이 포스팅은 아마 제가 Playwright 를 탐구하는 글이 될것같네요 ㅎ Playwright 란? Playwright 는 오픈소스 프레임워크로, E2E…","html":"<p>안녕하세요.</p>\n<p>프론트엔드하면서 부끄럽게도 테스트코드 작성이라는걸 말만 들어봤지 해본적이 없네요.</p>\n<p>부끄럽네요 ㅋ 이 포스팅은 아마 제가 Playwright 를 탐구하는 글이 될것같네요 ㅎ</p>\n<h1 id=\"playwright-란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#playwright-%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"playwright 란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Playwright 란?</h1>\n<p><strong>Playwright</strong> 는 오픈소스 프레임워크로, E2E 테스트를 위한 도구입니다.</p>\n<p>다양한 언어를 지원하구요. (TypeScript, JavaScript, Python, .NET, Java)</p>\n<p>모바일 웹 테스트도 된다고합니당. 이외에 여러가지 특징들이 있지만, 우선 저는 알못이기때문에 그냥 기초적인 정도만 서술해보려고합니다.</p>\n<p>저는 일단 프로젝트를 새로 만들어서 해보기로했어요.</p>\n<h1 id=\"프로젝트-생성-및-playwright-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-playwright-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 생성 및 playwright 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 생성 및 Playwright 설치</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>저는 pnpm을 주로 사용하고 있어서 패키지를 설치할 때 pnpm을 사용할거에요!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">pnpm</span> create vite</code></pre></div>\n<p>일단 vite react 프로젝트를 생성해용.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Project Name <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> react-playwright\nSelect a framework <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> React\nSelect a variant <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> TypeScript</code></pre></div>\n<p>저는 위와같이 선택하고 프로젝트를 만들었습니당.</p>\n<p>이제 playwright도 설치해염.</p>\n<p>리액트 프로젝트 디렉토리로 이동 후 다음 명령어 입력</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">pnpm</span> create playwright</code></pre></div>\n<p>위 명령어를 입력하면 나오는 프롬프트에서는 다음과 같이 선택했습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/f1512/bash01.webp 200w,\n/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/f59aa/bash01.webp 400w,\n/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/47a22/bash01.webp 800w,\n/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/925b7/bash01.webp 1146w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/f8f3a/bash01.png 200w,\n/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/6a8a8/bash01.png 400w,\n/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/7842b/bash01.png 800w,\n/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/601e5/bash01.png 1146w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b8bceb8a4d883254cd9d012e607bf36b/7842b/bash01.png\"\n            alt=\"bash01\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>조금 기다리면 설치가 끝나염.</p>\n<p>설치가 끝나면 다음과 같은 파일들이 생기는데여.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">playwright.config.ts         # playwright 설정파일\npackage.json\npackage-lock.json            # Or yarn.lock / pnpm-lock.yaml\ntests/\n  example.spec.ts            # 간단한 예제 테스트 파일\ntests-examples/\n  demo-todo-app.spec.ts      # 더 복잡한 예제 테스트 파일</code></pre></div>\n<p>간단한 예제 테스트 파일을 한번 살펴보겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> expect <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@playwright/test\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"has title\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> page <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> page<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">goto</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://playwright.dev/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Expect a title \"to contain\" a substring.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">expect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toHaveTitle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">Playwright</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"get started link\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> page <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> page<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">goto</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://playwright.dev/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Click the get started link.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> page<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getByRole</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"link\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Get started\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">click</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Expects page to have a heading with the name of Installation.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token function\">expect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    page<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getByRole</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"heading\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Installation\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toBeVisible</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">test</code> 와 <code class=\"language-text\">expect</code> 함수를 import 해서 사용하고있네요.</p>\n<p>아마도 <code class=\"language-text\">test</code> 함수는 테스트 케이스를 정의하고, <code class=\"language-text\">expect</code> 함수는 테스트 결과를 확인하는 함수일 것 같네요.</p>\n<p>우선 테스트를 실행하는 명령어부터 실행해보겠습니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"테스트-예제-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"테스트 예제 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>테스트 예제 실행</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">pnpm</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> playwright <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>저는 다음과 같은 결과가 나왔습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 628px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/f1512/test-result01.webp 200w,\n/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/f59aa/test-result01.webp 400w,\n/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/064a1/test-result01.webp 628w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/f8f3a/test-result01.png 200w,\n/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/6a8a8/test-result01.png 400w,\n/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/d67bd/test-result01.png 628w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/210bbd961cb07345deeaccfa28e69f8d/d67bd/test-result01.png\"\n            alt=\"test result01\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이미지에 적혀있는 <code class=\"language-text\">pnpm exec playwright show-report</code> 명령어를 실행해서 리포트를 확인해볼게요.</p>\n<h1 id=\"테스트-report-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-report-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"테스트 report 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>테스트 REPORT 확인</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">pnpm</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> playwright show-report</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/f1512/test-result02.webp 200w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/f59aa/test-result02.webp 400w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/47a22/test-result02.webp 800w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/5bb53/test-result02.webp 1200w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/485a2/test-result02.webp 1600w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/4aff1/test-result02.webp 2162w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/f8f3a/test-result02.png 200w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/6a8a8/test-result02.png 400w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/7842b/test-result02.png 800w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/5ece7/test-result02.png 1200w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/0d4f8/test-result02.png 1600w,\n/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/2b464/test-result02.png 2162w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6c768108a5aae07091cb7d716533770e/7842b/test-result02.png\"\n            alt=\"test result02\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>오.. 실행한 테스트에 대한 자세한 내용을 보여주는 웹 브라우저가 나타납니다.</p>\n<p>webkit, firefox, chromium 세 개 브라우저 환경에서 테스트를 실행했네요.</p>\n<p>목록에서 하나를 클릭해서 상세하게 내용을 확인해볼게요.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/f1512/test-result03.webp 200w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/f59aa/test-result03.webp 400w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/47a22/test-result03.webp 800w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/5bb53/test-result03.webp 1200w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/485a2/test-result03.webp 1600w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/ad408/test-result03.webp 2080w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/f8f3a/test-result03.png 200w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/6a8a8/test-result03.png 400w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/7842b/test-result03.png 800w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/5ece7/test-result03.png 1200w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/0d4f8/test-result03.png 1600w,\n/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/5c43f/test-result03.png 2080w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/b1a87c10a18f9c31e2a410966a3512e3/7842b/test-result03.png\"\n            alt=\"test result03\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>테스트 절차에 대해서 자세하게 내용을 확인할 수 있습니당.</p>\n<h1 id=\"ui-모드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ui-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"ui 모드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>UI 모드</h1>\n<p>공식문서를 살펴보니 테스트 결과를 웹 브라우저 UI로 확인할 수 있는 모드가 있습니다?</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">pnpm</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> playwright <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--ui</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위 명령어를 통해 ui모드로 테스트를 할 수 있어요.</p>\n<p>ui 모드로 테스트를 실행하면, 브라우저가 하나 실행되고 다음과 같은 이미지로 나타납니당.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/f1512/ui-mode.webp 200w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/f59aa/ui-mode.webp 400w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/47a22/ui-mode.webp 800w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/5bb53/ui-mode.webp 1200w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/485a2/ui-mode.webp 1600w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/eb2de/ui-mode.webp 2880w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/f8f3a/ui-mode.png 200w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/6a8a8/ui-mode.png 400w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/7842b/ui-mode.png 800w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/5ece7/ui-mode.png 1200w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/0d4f8/ui-mode.png 1600w,\n/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/c71fc/ui-mode.png 2880w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/9761c4dfb822d74ce42c2c83a5cb31f0/7842b/ui-mode.png\"\n            alt=\"ui mode\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>직접 브라우저를 보면서, 테스트 코드가 어떻게 진행되는지 확인할 수 있어서 좋은것같네여.</p>\n<hr />\n<h1 id=\"마무리하며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"마무리하며 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마무리하며</h1>\n<p>요번 글에서는 대충 프로젝트 만들고 Playwright 깔고 playwright로 어떻게 테스트를 진행하는지 정도 확인해봤구여.</p>\n<p>앞으로도 공식문서를 따라가면서 공부하면서 기록할것같네요.</p>\n<p>감사합니당.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#playwright-%EB%9E%80\">Playwright 란?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-playwright-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%